WEBVTT

00:00:00.830 --> 00:00:04.120
Her name was Natsumi-san.

00:00:04.120 --> 00:00:06.370
Goroku orchestrated everything.

00:00:06.370 --> 00:00:09.490
If my husband catches on,
Goroku will kill him.

00:00:09.490 --> 00:00:11.480
Elections are coming up, no?

00:00:11.480 --> 00:00:14.160
The money will go to Yaichi Makita.

00:00:14.160 --> 00:00:16.980
His party must win at any cost.

00:00:16.980 --> 00:00:20.950
Please, let me see Takumi before I go.

00:00:20.950 --> 00:00:22.730
Unfortunately, that won't be possible.

00:00:22.730 --> 00:00:26.210
Fuyuhashi and his people
already have you surrounded.

00:00:29.130 --> 00:00:32.010
Apologize to Machi on your way to hell.

00:00:39.300 --> 00:00:42.040
Run to the parking lot!

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:53.040
Timing and subtitles by
"🍰 The Pastry Detectives 🔍" Team @Viki.com

00:01:38.170 --> 00:01:39.890
Get in!

00:01:41.970 --> 00:01:43.810
Hurry!

00:01:57.540 --> 00:01:58.790
We're getting off.

00:01:58.790 --> 00:02:02.040
Our location is still compromised.

00:02:04.080 --> 00:02:05.880
Hurry.

00:02:07.020 --> 00:02:08.940
Why did you come?

00:02:08.940 --> 00:02:10.740
Why wouldn't I protect my wife?

00:02:10.740 --> 00:02:14.450
I told you, I'm not your wife.

00:02:24.920 --> 00:02:27.430
Were you also bugged?

00:02:29.660 --> 00:02:31.800
He's blackmailing you, isn't he?

00:02:34.610 --> 00:02:36.760
I know you're Natsumi.

00:02:37.570 --> 00:02:38.720
I told you, I'm not...

00:02:38.720 --> 00:02:41.740
The Shinowa Cafe at Minami-Rinkan.

00:02:41.740 --> 00:02:44.320
That's where we first spoke.

00:02:47.030 --> 00:02:50.150
I invited you to come cafe-hopping with me.

00:02:50.150 --> 00:02:52.380
Remember Emer in Kyobashi?

00:02:53.690 --> 00:02:56.630
Now that place blew our taste buds off.

00:03:01.420 --> 00:03:05.690
Don't you miss my Hayase Shortcake?

00:03:11.830 --> 00:03:14.450
Don't you miss Takumi?

00:03:16.310 --> 00:03:20.560
He insisted you were alive,
all three years you were gone.

00:03:22.790 --> 00:03:25.490
Even after we found your corpse,

00:03:25.490 --> 00:03:27.750
he fought through his sorrow

00:03:27.750 --> 00:03:31.150
to protect the store you loved.

00:03:31.920 --> 00:03:34.250
You were watching, weren't you?

00:03:37.150 --> 00:03:40.520
He never gives in to his bullies.

00:03:41.280 --> 00:03:43.870
He's still waiting for us to come home.

00:03:46.340 --> 00:03:50.540
He misses you with all his heart.

00:03:50.540 --> 00:03:53.450
He loves you, Natsumi.

00:03:53.450 --> 00:03:56.240
He could never forget about you.

00:03:57.940 --> 00:04:02.300
Don't you want to see your Takumi again?

00:04:05.380 --> 00:04:07.200
Of course I do.

00:04:11.260 --> 00:04:13.550
I want to hold him close and never let go.

00:04:15.970 --> 00:04:17.300
Natsumi...

00:04:17.300 --> 00:04:19.720
I'm so sorry.

00:04:19.720 --> 00:04:22.500
I didn't mean to get you involved.

00:04:23.220 --> 00:04:25.650
I'm so, so sorry.

00:04:33.140 --> 00:04:35.060
Thank god...

00:04:36.720 --> 00:04:39.100
You're alive...

00:04:42.510 --> 00:04:45.130
Thank god...

00:04:53.410 --> 00:04:56.510
I will end my life as "Ichika Kogo."

00:04:57.250 --> 00:05:00.500
Takumi and your mother
are in danger if I stay.

00:05:04.020 --> 00:05:05.810
At least I got to see you.

00:05:05.810 --> 00:05:08.410
Don't even humor that idea.

00:05:08.410 --> 00:05:10.680
We're going home together.

00:05:10.680 --> 00:05:12.640
We can't.

00:05:12.640 --> 00:05:15.920
My actions caused your mother to get hurt.

00:05:17.600 --> 00:05:19.650
I could never go to see Takumi.

00:05:20.440 --> 00:05:24.580
He's better off not knowing
his mother was a criminal.

00:05:26.790 --> 00:05:29.940
That's not your choice to make.

00:05:31.260 --> 00:05:36.140
Mom and Takumi will decide
how they judge you themselves.

00:05:36.960 --> 00:05:42.240
You have to go home and talk to them.

00:05:42.240 --> 00:05:44.630
Goroku will hunt down our family.

00:05:44.630 --> 00:05:46.430
I won't let him.

00:05:46.430 --> 00:05:49.040
I'll crush him and the entire organization.

00:05:49.040 --> 00:05:51.660
That's impossible.

00:05:51.660 --> 00:05:53.830
Don't give up.

00:05:55.470 --> 00:05:58.620
Hayase's are known for their tenacity, right?

00:06:04.260 --> 00:06:07.270
I finally have an ally I can trust.

00:06:07.270 --> 00:06:09.950
Nothing is more heartening than that.

00:06:11.290 --> 00:06:13.860
Let's find a path back home together.

00:06:15.190 --> 00:06:17.440
We can do this.

00:06:19.750 --> 00:06:21.640
Natsumi.

00:06:42.500 --> 00:06:45.500
This marks our brand new reboot.

00:07:11.840 --> 00:07:21.200
[Riku and Natsumi Hayase, Reboot, Day 1]

00:07:24.420 --> 00:07:26.240
Some of it was already turned into cash.

00:07:26.240 --> 00:07:31.230
Ichika-chan was liquidating the riches bit by bit.

00:07:31.230 --> 00:07:33.030
Is that so?

00:07:38.080 --> 00:07:39.760
- Kaieda-san, excuse me.
- Yes?

00:07:39.760 --> 00:07:41.940
Right.

00:07:46.660 --> 00:07:49.380
My wife told me everything.

00:07:50.510 --> 00:07:54.200
You're in a bind
now that the ten billion was found.

00:07:54.200 --> 00:07:58.000
If Mr. Ma catches on, you're a dead man.

00:07:58.000 --> 00:08:02.090
Good thing Mr. Ma would never believe you.

00:08:02.090 --> 00:08:05.710
But you also can't return the money to him.

00:08:05.710 --> 00:08:09.690
You need to back Yaichi Makita, after all.

00:08:11.090 --> 00:08:13.840
I have no idea what you're talking about.

00:08:13.840 --> 00:08:18.520
You'll pay for messing with my family.

00:08:18.520 --> 00:08:21.760
And what can you two do?

00:08:23.610 --> 00:08:28.210
I know you didn't want us working together.

00:08:28.210 --> 00:08:32.520
That's why you painted Natsumi
in a bad light.

00:08:33.420 --> 00:08:37.660
You'll regret making an enemy of the Hayase's.

00:08:40.530 --> 00:08:41.580
[Gido: Tracking location...]
[Ichika Kogo: Tracking location...]

00:08:41.580 --> 00:08:43.870
[Gido: Offline]
[Ichika Kogo: Offline]

00:09:02.950 --> 00:09:04.120
Sir?

00:09:04.120 --> 00:09:07.600
Adachi, you got a false lead.
Try somewhere else.

00:09:21.320 --> 00:09:23.410
Could you two also look into this woman?

00:09:23.410 --> 00:09:24.420
[Ichika Kogo, Financial Advisor]

00:09:24.420 --> 00:09:26.590
"Ichika Kogo."

00:09:40.220 --> 00:09:42.290
Gido...

00:09:50.280 --> 00:09:52.250
Hello?

00:09:52.250 --> 00:09:54.840
I apologize for calling at this late hour.

00:09:56.770 --> 00:09:58.660
Who is this?

00:09:58.660 --> 00:10:01.010
It was Hayase.

00:10:01.010 --> 00:10:05.350
He betrayed us and helped Ichika escape.

00:10:06.140 --> 00:10:08.940
Why did he save Ichika-chan?

00:10:08.940 --> 00:10:10.720
Were they an item?

00:10:10.720 --> 00:10:12.800
I doubt it.

00:10:12.800 --> 00:10:16.630
She was dating Gido-san. It's possible.

00:10:16.630 --> 00:10:20.170
Right, they do have the same face.

00:10:20.170 --> 00:10:22.620
This is no time for jokes.

00:10:23.400 --> 00:10:25.010
My apologies, Sir.

00:10:25.010 --> 00:10:26.930
Deal with them.

00:10:26.930 --> 00:10:29.600
I don't care what methods you use.

00:10:29.600 --> 00:10:33.320
I'll put a hundred million
on each of their heads.

00:10:33.320 --> 00:10:35.200
And one more thing.

00:10:36.300 --> 00:10:42.090
We will not inform Mr. Ma of the ten billion.

00:10:43.490 --> 00:10:46.350
Gido stole the riches,
and the money went missing.

00:10:46.350 --> 00:10:50.760
We cannot tarnish our image any further.

00:10:53.480 --> 00:10:55.700
Am I clear? This is an order.

00:10:55.700 --> 00:10:56.830
Yes, Sir.

00:10:56.830 --> 00:11:00.950
Find Ichika and Hayase at once.

00:11:17.420 --> 00:11:18.910
What?

00:11:18.910 --> 00:11:23.000
Part of the ten billion
had already been cashed in.

00:11:23.000 --> 00:11:25.610
Goroku-san

00:11:25.610 --> 00:11:29.730
hopes to liquidate the rest, immediately.

00:11:29.730 --> 00:11:32.200
Can I count on you to handle it?

00:11:32.200 --> 00:11:37.950
What? If Mr. Ma found out,
my head would go flying, too!

00:11:37.950 --> 00:11:39.930
Kikuchi-san.

00:11:40.750 --> 00:11:46.150
Truth be told, I plan on leaving backstage

00:11:46.150 --> 00:11:50.130
to focus my efforts in the spotlight.

00:11:50.130 --> 00:11:54.380
This organization will need a new leader.

00:12:05.920 --> 00:12:10.610
Hold off on killing her.
She might be Natsumi.

00:12:22.370 --> 00:12:24.390
Evening.

00:12:28.720 --> 00:12:30.810
Where's Machi?

00:12:30.810 --> 00:12:33.150
I transported her to Shelter.

00:12:44.330 --> 00:12:47.990
Mom, please protect Dad.

00:12:52.870 --> 00:12:54.700
I washed the dishes.

00:12:54.700 --> 00:12:56.760
Thank you.

00:12:56.760 --> 00:12:58.710
I have the choux shells chilling here.

00:12:58.710 --> 00:13:01.920
I'll help fill them after school.

00:13:01.920 --> 00:13:03.470
Yes, Chef!

00:13:03.470 --> 00:13:06.390
- See you later.
- Have a good day.

00:13:30.870 --> 00:13:32.090
Takumi!

00:13:32.090 --> 00:13:35.460
Let go of him, you bastard!

00:13:40.020 --> 00:13:43.000
I'm with the police!

00:13:47.020 --> 00:13:48.910
There are three of them!

00:13:48.910 --> 00:13:50.980
Yes, Sir!

00:13:51.790 --> 00:13:53.400
Adachi!

00:13:57.080 --> 00:13:59.900
- You all right?
- Yes, Sir.

00:13:59.900 --> 00:14:01.390
You're strong.

00:14:01.390 --> 00:14:03.810
I was trained in the academy.

00:14:06.420 --> 00:14:07.910
Excuse me.

00:14:07.910 --> 00:14:09.410
Takumi!

00:14:09.410 --> 00:14:12.340
- Takumi!
- Grandma...

00:14:14.490 --> 00:14:16.660
What's going on?

00:14:17.750 --> 00:14:19.530
We got a tip.

00:14:19.530 --> 00:14:21.260
A tip?

00:14:21.260 --> 00:14:23.200
- Teramoto.
- Yes, Sir.

00:14:23.200 --> 00:14:25.010
Walk Takumi-kun back.

00:14:25.780 --> 00:14:28.070
Let's wait in the store, okay?

00:14:28.070 --> 00:14:30.110
No, I'm listening.

00:14:40.850 --> 00:14:44.960
The report claimed your safety
was currently being compromised.

00:14:44.960 --> 00:14:46.290
What? Why?

00:14:46.290 --> 00:14:47.660
We do not know.

00:14:47.660 --> 00:14:52.620
But the caller insisted this was tied
to Natsumi-san's case.

00:14:52.620 --> 00:14:54.450
Who is this?

00:14:54.450 --> 00:14:57.050
I am Riku Hayase.

00:14:57.050 --> 00:14:59.840
He identified himself as Riku Hayase.

00:15:01.180 --> 00:15:03.270
Dad...

00:15:04.140 --> 00:15:09.480
Rest easy.
Our officers will protect you both.

00:15:09.480 --> 00:15:12.920
We'll need you both to stay home for the day.

00:15:13.680 --> 00:15:17.240
I'll keep watch for the time being.

00:15:17.240 --> 00:15:18.750
How did it go?

00:15:18.750 --> 00:15:20.920
The police were guarding him.

00:15:20.920 --> 00:15:23.350
Hayase's the one who gave the order.

00:15:23.350 --> 00:15:26.830
He jumped in to help as well.

00:15:26.830 --> 00:15:30.110
We owe our police insider for the intel.

00:15:30.110 --> 00:15:35.330
Not to worry, Sir.
None of these lackeys have ties to us.

00:15:35.330 --> 00:15:39.020
We're lucky Hayase showed up. Capture him.

00:15:39.020 --> 00:15:40.640
Yes, Sir.

00:15:46.590 --> 00:15:52.630
Thank you for your work.
[Police]

00:15:54.660 --> 00:15:58.240
All right, time to interrogate these chumps.

00:15:58.240 --> 00:15:59.600
We're leaving, Gido.

00:15:59.600 --> 00:16:01.070
Sorry, Chief.

00:16:01.070 --> 00:16:03.150
I'm staying to guard the Hayase's.

00:16:03.150 --> 00:16:04.700
Don't worry about them.

00:16:04.700 --> 00:16:08.920
I can't help it. I'm a fan of their pastries.

00:16:12.520 --> 00:16:14.180
Sir.

00:16:15.390 --> 00:16:16.970
What's up?

00:16:26.610 --> 00:16:31.540
This is in front of Hitomi Plastic Surgery.

00:16:31.540 --> 00:16:35.140
It's a shot of you walking out their doors,

00:16:35.140 --> 00:16:37.730
six months after Natsumi-san was found.

00:16:41.690 --> 00:16:44.570
You returned to the office
soon after this date.

00:16:48.380 --> 00:16:50.130
Adachi.

00:16:53.050 --> 00:16:55.970
What does justice mean to you?

00:16:57.000 --> 00:16:58.640
Pardon?

00:16:58.640 --> 00:17:02.620
Natsumi-san's case
is tied to Goroku's organization.

00:17:02.620 --> 00:17:06.130
But a traitor in the police
is feeding him intel.

00:17:06.130 --> 00:17:10.000
We can't crush Goroku without finding them.

00:17:12.260 --> 00:17:14.660
Do you have any proof?

00:17:18.550 --> 00:17:20.660
No. Call it a detective's hunch.

00:17:22.460 --> 00:17:25.300
I want you to find this traitor.

00:17:26.770 --> 00:17:30.290
Why would you entrust such an important task
to a rookie like me?

00:17:30.290 --> 00:17:33.940
Because I believe
you're on the side of justice.

00:17:37.110 --> 00:17:41.090
But Sir... How?

00:17:47.710 --> 00:17:49.320
Adachi.

00:17:51.720 --> 00:17:57.350
Do our locker rooms
have security cameras in them?

00:17:57.350 --> 00:18:00.250
I believe so.

00:18:01.150 --> 00:18:03.470
We're leaving, Adachi.

00:18:03.470 --> 00:18:06.150
Adachi, listen.

00:18:06.150 --> 00:18:09.620
Someone planted a laptop in my locker
when I came back to the office.

00:18:09.620 --> 00:18:12.350
That's our traitor.

00:18:12.350 --> 00:18:14.190
Look through those security tapes.

00:18:14.190 --> 00:18:16.620
You have to help me out.

00:18:16.620 --> 00:18:18.160
I'm counting on you.

00:18:26.240 --> 00:18:27.330
Gido-san...

00:18:27.330 --> 00:18:29.260
May I have a moment?

00:18:34.300 --> 00:18:36.280
Please close the shop for now.

00:18:36.280 --> 00:18:38.530
Try not to leave the house either.

00:18:39.380 --> 00:18:42.120
Will you stay with us?

00:18:44.730 --> 00:18:46.340
Sorry.

00:18:46.340 --> 00:18:48.290
I came to leave from that window.

00:18:48.290 --> 00:18:50.590
What? Why the window?

00:18:50.590 --> 00:18:53.660
I can't have the culprit finding me.

00:18:57.570 --> 00:19:02.240
Don't worry.
Our officers will keep you two safe.

00:19:08.030 --> 00:19:10.180
You can relax, Grandma.

00:19:10.180 --> 00:19:12.550
I'll protect you.

00:19:14.120 --> 00:19:16.260
Taku-chan...

00:19:16.260 --> 00:19:19.650
I promise we'll be okay.

00:19:20.870 --> 00:19:22.600
We'll be okay.

00:19:24.270 --> 00:19:27.240
So don't worry, okay?

00:19:28.250 --> 00:19:30.010
Takumi.

00:19:48.400 --> 00:19:50.810
You've become strong, kid.

00:19:58.610 --> 00:20:03.730
Hayase's are known for being tenacious.
Isn't that right?

00:20:05.590 --> 00:20:08.300
It can't be. Are you...

00:20:08.300 --> 00:20:10.690
Take care of your grandma, okay?

00:20:56.610 --> 00:20:58.450
Were they okay?

00:20:58.450 --> 00:21:02.750
Goroku went after them, but I stopped him.

00:21:02.750 --> 00:21:07.080
The police will guard them.
They're safe for now.

00:21:07.940 --> 00:21:10.850
I hope Takumi will be all right...

00:21:10.850 --> 00:21:13.720
He seemed so anxious.

00:21:13.720 --> 00:21:16.050
I ended up pulling his ears.

00:21:17.640 --> 00:21:19.480
I see.

00:21:21.480 --> 00:21:24.000
How did he react?

00:21:24.000 --> 00:21:26.590
He was frozen in shock.

00:21:26.590 --> 00:21:29.710
Just like the first time he tried ice cream.

00:21:29.710 --> 00:21:32.160
And don't forget cotton candy.

00:21:33.210 --> 00:21:35.220
Our cute boy.

00:21:35.220 --> 00:21:37.750
Remember how his eyes shot wide open?

00:21:41.160 --> 00:21:43.810
I didn't tell him about you.

00:21:48.770 --> 00:21:52.620
I really don't think I should return.

00:21:52.620 --> 00:21:55.310
I'd only destroy the family.

00:21:57.780 --> 00:22:00.590
You're a part of "the family," too.

00:22:03.780 --> 00:22:04.950
All right, let's hurry.

00:22:04.950 --> 00:22:07.030
We'll finish this while they're safe.

00:22:07.030 --> 00:22:10.650
I want to guarantee Ayaka's safety as well.

00:22:11.580 --> 00:22:13.380
Of course.

00:22:26.290 --> 00:22:29.410
They're here.

00:22:32.680 --> 00:22:35.420
Hello there.

00:22:35.420 --> 00:22:37.490
This is my wife, Hazuki.

00:22:37.490 --> 00:22:41.000
And this is Inspector Gido-san and Kogo-san.

00:22:41.000 --> 00:22:43.050
Nice to meet you both.

00:22:43.050 --> 00:22:45.170
We apologize for interrupting
your weekend, Ma'am.

00:22:45.170 --> 00:22:47.600
Sorry, this will be quick.

00:22:47.600 --> 00:22:49.210
Inspector Gido,

00:22:49.210 --> 00:22:52.200
please let me enjoy my days off.

00:22:53.180 --> 00:22:56.650
Still, perhaps my home gives us privacy.

00:22:56.650 --> 00:23:00.270
Excuse me, is my sister...

00:23:01.180 --> 00:23:05.810
My subordinates are watching her
for her connections to "Gido."

00:23:05.810 --> 00:23:07.130
Ayaka Kogo-san will be safe.

00:23:07.130 --> 00:23:09.630
We've almost returned.

00:23:10.940 --> 00:23:13.420
Thank you.

00:23:13.420 --> 00:23:17.920
I'm surprised you worry about her.
She's a stranger to you, isn't she?

00:23:17.920 --> 00:23:21.310
She is my younger sister.

00:23:21.310 --> 00:23:23.230
I've been filled in on the situation.

00:23:23.230 --> 00:23:26.330
I know you've changed your face, as well.

00:23:26.330 --> 00:23:32.220
My wife can testify
about Goroku's tie to Yaichi.

00:23:33.270 --> 00:23:35.310
I must first make this known.

00:23:35.310 --> 00:23:40.780
If we arrest both Goroku and my brother,
Hayase-san will surely be pardoned.

00:23:40.780 --> 00:23:45.920
But the same cannot be said
about you, Natsumi-san.

00:23:45.920 --> 00:23:49.100
I'm prepared to atone for my sins.

00:23:49.100 --> 00:23:50.900
Please, save my husband.

00:23:50.900 --> 00:23:56.080
Our whole family will wait
for her to return home.

00:23:59.990 --> 00:24:01.960
What a loving relationship.

00:24:01.960 --> 00:24:03.860
I'm jealous.

00:24:04.650 --> 00:24:07.980
My wife and I struggle in that regard.

00:24:08.690 --> 00:24:11.190
Twelve years ago,

00:24:11.190 --> 00:24:14.970
my wife committed a hit-and-run,

00:24:14.970 --> 00:24:18.310
which severely stunted my career.

00:24:18.310 --> 00:24:21.100
She feels responsible for my fate, even now.

00:24:21.100 --> 00:24:24.590
I must move up the ladder

00:24:24.590 --> 00:24:27.770
so she can smile again.

00:24:29.080 --> 00:24:31.310
Goroku wishes to donate

00:24:31.310 --> 00:24:34.630
a large sum of money to Yaichi Makita.

00:24:34.630 --> 00:24:35.920
Is that correct?

00:24:35.920 --> 00:24:37.250
Yes.

00:24:37.250 --> 00:24:42.530
Goroku can have his associate, Kikuchi,
liquidate the riches at any time.

00:24:42.530 --> 00:24:44.890
Yaichi will be quick to receive the money.

00:24:44.890 --> 00:24:49.190
Then we will aim to catch them during the deal.

00:24:49.190 --> 00:24:53.440
Goroku will rush the deal
so Mr. Ma won't catch on.

00:24:53.440 --> 00:24:57.780
Please have the Second Investigation Team
keep eyes on Kikuchi.

00:25:00.110 --> 00:25:04.160
I would, but Goroku has a spy
within our ranks.

00:25:04.160 --> 00:25:07.340
If he learns of our plan, it's over.

00:25:07.340 --> 00:25:12.970
I'll need you both to figure out
when this deal is happening first.

00:25:14.140 --> 00:25:15.750
But how...

00:25:15.750 --> 00:25:19.850
You'll have to get one of
Goroku's people on your side.

00:25:22.300 --> 00:25:25.040
I'll try speaking to Fuyuhashi.

00:25:29.030 --> 00:25:33.310
He might join us
once he knows Goroku killed Machi.

00:25:33.310 --> 00:25:34.740
I'll come with you.

00:25:34.740 --> 00:25:38.550
You can't. He'll kill you on the spot.

00:25:38.550 --> 00:25:41.390
I can at least speak to him.

00:25:43.690 --> 00:25:46.220
Here, use these.

00:25:46.940 --> 00:25:49.700
Each phone tracks the other's location.

00:25:49.700 --> 00:25:52.450
They transmit surrounding sounds as well.

00:25:52.450 --> 00:25:57.830
Though our current statistics
have the dominant party leading,

00:25:57.830 --> 00:26:03.080
Yaichi Makita's party is slowly,
yet surely gaining momentum.

00:26:03.080 --> 00:26:07.870
Elections are next month.

00:26:07.870 --> 00:26:10.450
Will there be a party upset?

00:26:10.450 --> 00:26:11.800
Onto our next headline.

00:26:11.800 --> 00:26:14.120
Rising costs of foodstuffs are...

00:26:19.040 --> 00:26:21.260
Citizens of Japan want you

00:26:21.950 --> 00:26:25.000
as their Prime Minister, Mr. Makita.

00:26:26.560 --> 00:26:30.740
We cannot let this chance evade us.

00:26:31.620 --> 00:26:33.100
Yes.

00:26:34.160 --> 00:26:37.130
Citizens are fed up with current politicians

00:26:37.130 --> 00:26:39.900
who only prioritize

00:26:39.900 --> 00:26:42.750
certain special-interest groups.
[Yaichi Makita]

00:26:42.750 --> 00:26:44.950
We must make our move now.

00:26:44.950 --> 00:26:47.120
And to that end...

00:26:47.120 --> 00:26:49.590
Yes. The ten billion yen.

00:26:49.590 --> 00:26:53.440
I'll have it ready by tomorrow.

00:26:54.670 --> 00:26:57.940
If I donate to your nominees,

00:26:59.170 --> 00:27:01.100
you will become the dominant party, yes?

00:27:02.550 --> 00:27:07.180
Of course, I will become prime minister.

00:27:11.260 --> 00:27:17.580
This transaction of mine
comes with quite a bit of risk.

00:27:18.810 --> 00:27:22.280
The police are already on my tail.

00:27:22.280 --> 00:27:27.190
This money is necessary for Japan's survival.

00:27:27.190 --> 00:27:30.650
I will emerge victorious
and assuage their suspicions.

00:27:30.650 --> 00:27:35.050
Only then will I come to make an appeal.

00:27:35.050 --> 00:27:38.650
We must move this country
in a better direction.

00:27:41.550 --> 00:27:44.400
Politics and dirty money

00:27:44.400 --> 00:27:47.780
are characterized by promises and rewards.

00:27:47.780 --> 00:27:53.420
Yet you've never once come to me
for any sort of compensation.

00:27:53.420 --> 00:27:55.960
You almost had a self-sacrificial mentality,

00:27:55.960 --> 00:27:59.250
but that is precisely why

00:27:59.250 --> 00:28:03.610
I felt inclined to trust you.

00:28:05.160 --> 00:28:09.980
So long as money is used properly,
this country can start anew.

00:28:09.980 --> 00:28:12.700
Efficiently utilize our citizen's tax money,

00:28:12.700 --> 00:28:16.540
reduce tax rates,
and combat the declining birth rate.

00:28:16.540 --> 00:28:22.040
Politicians are destroying this nation
by ignoring our countrymen.

00:28:22.040 --> 00:28:24.460
We must eliminate the rot from within

00:28:24.460 --> 00:28:27.060
and reboot this country.

00:28:27.060 --> 00:28:30.620
Your ten billion is an investment.

00:28:31.530 --> 00:28:35.550
Thankfully, anything is cheaper

00:28:35.550 --> 00:28:38.140
than our national budget of 115 trillion yen.

00:28:41.650 --> 00:28:44.890
I am prepared to use

00:28:44.890 --> 00:28:48.340
any means necessary to save this country.

00:28:59.590 --> 00:29:01.160
Aoi.

00:29:03.400 --> 00:29:06.450
I leave Shelter in your hands.

00:29:08.540 --> 00:29:10.360
I'm sure Machi...

00:29:12.780 --> 00:29:15.160
would've wanted the same.

00:29:17.380 --> 00:29:18.800
Yes.

00:29:38.240 --> 00:29:40.440
Don't move!

00:29:40.440 --> 00:29:41.660
Don't move.

00:29:41.660 --> 00:29:44.350
I need to talk to Fuyuhashi-san. Wait outside.

00:29:44.350 --> 00:29:46.420
You bastard...

00:29:46.420 --> 00:29:49.990
Wait in front of the car where I can see you.

00:29:49.990 --> 00:29:52.550
Leave your gun here.

00:29:52.550 --> 00:29:54.260
Leave it.

00:30:04.150 --> 00:30:06.470
Hayase's in the car.

00:30:09.300 --> 00:30:12.070
Ichika Kogo was Natsumi.

00:30:13.330 --> 00:30:17.050
Goroku's the one who stole the ten billion.

00:30:18.270 --> 00:30:22.020
He had Natsumi hire those part-timers
to guard the safe.

00:30:22.020 --> 00:30:24.730
Natsumi's not your enemy.

00:30:24.730 --> 00:30:26.540
It's Goroku.

00:30:32.330 --> 00:30:34.440
Fuyuhashi.

00:30:35.960 --> 00:30:38.900
Work with us to crush Goroku.

00:30:43.470 --> 00:30:46.180
You take over the organization.

00:30:46.180 --> 00:30:49.470
Grant Machi's dreams with the money.

00:30:52.420 --> 00:30:57.600
You're still as clueless as ever.

00:30:58.380 --> 00:30:59.910
Listen up.

00:30:59.910 --> 00:31:03.690
Our world has no business with "the truth."

00:31:04.430 --> 00:31:06.800
We only care about "reality."

00:31:06.800 --> 00:31:08.310
Machi was murdered.

00:31:08.310 --> 00:31:10.780
The culprit was in contact with Ichika.

00:31:10.780 --> 00:31:14.660
Goroku-san ordered us to kill Ichika.

00:31:14.660 --> 00:31:19.600
He then ordered us to kill you
for letting Ichika go.

00:31:19.600 --> 00:31:21.240
Those are the facts.

00:31:21.240 --> 00:31:22.660
You're playing into Goroku's hands.

00:31:22.660 --> 00:31:26.050
No one can know
the hidden truth of a situation.

00:31:27.080 --> 00:31:32.410
Reality is twisted
because of our imagination.

00:31:32.410 --> 00:31:36.900
It's only right to judge
what I see with my own eyes.

00:31:36.900 --> 00:31:41.080
You'd be avenging Machi.

00:31:41.080 --> 00:31:44.900
The ones who really killed Machi
were those who gave up on her.

00:31:44.900 --> 00:31:47.210
If you need someone to blame...

00:31:48.440 --> 00:31:51.430
Blame me, for inviting her into this world.

00:31:56.440 --> 00:31:59.310
Then what's next for you?

00:32:01.440 --> 00:32:03.560
Will you continue to be Goroku's dog,

00:32:03.560 --> 00:32:06.280
killing and burying people in mountains,

00:32:06.280 --> 00:32:08.250
for the rest of your damn life?

00:32:09.730 --> 00:32:12.290
When you started Shelter,

00:32:12.290 --> 00:32:16.370
you wanted to create a place for lost kids.

00:32:16.370 --> 00:32:18.830
That's what you told Natsumi, right?

00:32:19.970 --> 00:32:22.160
Was all that a lie?

00:32:27.530 --> 00:32:30.420
Fuyuhashi. Make a choice, for your family.

00:32:30.420 --> 00:32:35.200
If you want to save them, leave Goroku!

00:32:39.750 --> 00:32:42.640
That's a hundred million for us.

00:32:45.110 --> 00:32:47.990
Using local ingredients from Yakushima,

00:32:47.990 --> 00:32:51.940
we will give guests a taste
of the regional cuisine.

00:32:51.940 --> 00:32:54.240
As for activities...

00:32:54.240 --> 00:32:57.870
Sorry folks, I'm flying to Yakushima.

00:32:59.970 --> 00:33:01.470
Hello?

00:33:01.470 --> 00:33:03.180
We captured Hayase.

00:33:03.180 --> 00:33:05.880
Great work.

00:33:05.880 --> 00:33:08.600
Did he mention any reason why

00:33:08.600 --> 00:33:11.120
he let Ichika escape?

00:33:12.450 --> 00:33:16.270
No, Sir. We did him in before he could speak.

00:33:16.270 --> 00:33:18.450
But he's still alive.

00:33:18.450 --> 00:33:20.280
Shall I finish the job?

00:33:20.280 --> 00:33:23.650
No, make it look like a suicide.

00:33:23.650 --> 00:33:25.270
Yes, Sir.

00:33:25.270 --> 00:33:27.590
I'll transport him to his place right away.

00:33:31.950 --> 00:33:33.950
You're as speedy as ever, Kikuchi!

00:33:33.950 --> 00:33:36.590
Thanks a million.

00:33:36.590 --> 00:33:40.540
See you tomorrow.

00:33:41.270 --> 00:33:43.330
Ichika-chan?

00:33:45.000 --> 00:33:48.850
What, you've come to rely on me after all?

00:33:48.850 --> 00:33:52.070
But you're too late. The money is all gone...

00:33:52.850 --> 00:33:54.200
Wow, nelly.

00:33:54.200 --> 00:33:56.020
Sit.

00:33:57.900 --> 00:34:03.390
No need to restrict me.
I won't pounce on you!

00:34:03.390 --> 00:34:06.900
I'm always nice and gentle with the ladies.

00:34:06.900 --> 00:34:10.470
Goroku must have let you handle the money.

00:34:10.470 --> 00:34:15.160
That's between me and my client.

00:34:23.000 --> 00:34:24.700
[Kikuchi]

00:34:24.700 --> 00:34:28.190
I knew it. Kikuchi is liquidating everything.

00:34:30.410 --> 00:34:33.160
Goroku's the one who stole the ten billion.

00:34:33.160 --> 00:34:36.120
He wants to give that money to a politician.

00:34:36.120 --> 00:34:38.580
Surely he's told you, right?

00:34:39.750 --> 00:34:43.660
When and where is the deal happening?

00:34:48.810 --> 00:34:52.150
If I betray Goroku-san this time,
I'd be killed for sure.

00:34:52.150 --> 00:34:57.230
I'd much rather die by your pretty hands.

00:35:01.510 --> 00:35:06.150
Four years ago,
I looked into your bank account.

00:35:06.150 --> 00:35:09.330
You were sending part of your embezzled money

00:35:09.330 --> 00:35:14.890
to a "Kimie Shimizu" every month.

00:35:14.890 --> 00:35:18.350
Kimie was your former wife.
You two even had a son.

00:35:18.350 --> 00:35:24.110
You purposefully distanced yourself,
yet continued to pay child support.

00:35:27.200 --> 00:35:29.130
What're you going on about?

00:35:29.130 --> 00:35:32.260
Don't you recall begging at my feet?

00:35:33.780 --> 00:35:37.360
You said if Goroku found out,
he'd take your family hostage.

00:35:37.360 --> 00:35:40.660
You begged me not to rat you out.

00:35:41.910 --> 00:35:44.430
How do you know all that?

00:35:44.430 --> 00:35:46.520
You still haven't caught on?

00:35:52.740 --> 00:35:54.510
No...

00:35:55.480 --> 00:35:57.970
I don't believe it.

00:35:58.980 --> 00:36:01.310
Is it really you?

00:36:01.310 --> 00:36:03.720
Are you Natsumi-chan?

00:36:04.740 --> 00:36:09.330
I became Ichika-san
because he took my family hostage.

00:36:09.330 --> 00:36:12.100
I even got my husband involved in this mess.

00:36:12.950 --> 00:36:17.000
I've had enough. I'm ending Goroku's reign.

00:36:17.000 --> 00:36:18.380
Impossible.

00:36:18.380 --> 00:36:20.330
You don't stand a chance.

00:36:20.330 --> 00:36:25.510
The billion from three years ago
was also Goroku's doing.

00:36:25.510 --> 00:36:29.270
He pinned the blame on you
and left you half-dead.

00:36:29.270 --> 00:36:32.280
We both have a motive against Goroku.

00:36:36.600 --> 00:36:40.140
Tell me when and where the deal is happening.

00:36:40.140 --> 00:36:43.290
I want to return my husband to his family.

00:36:43.290 --> 00:36:44.980
Please.

00:36:52.260 --> 00:36:56.170
Put the gun to my head again.

00:36:56.170 --> 00:36:58.400
Hurry.

00:36:58.400 --> 00:37:01.330
I don't want to die!

00:37:01.330 --> 00:37:04.000
If I don't speak, she'll kill me!

00:37:07.540 --> 00:37:10.350
Don't worry, no one's listening in.

00:37:10.350 --> 00:37:14.110
I just wanted a reason
to disobey my contract.

00:37:14.110 --> 00:37:16.930
Corrupted as I may be, I'm still a lawyer.

00:37:16.930 --> 00:37:19.250
Kikuchi-chan's already liquidated the riches.

00:37:19.250 --> 00:37:21.640
The bills weigh just over a ton.

00:37:21.640 --> 00:37:24.990
He's packing them in a truck
to be shipped right to our client.

00:37:24.990 --> 00:37:27.390
The deal starts at 6 p.m. tomorrow.

00:37:27.390 --> 00:37:33.100
It's happening at an office in Machida,
owned by Yaichi Makita.

00:37:33.100 --> 00:37:37.370
The deal will be supervised by myself
and their secretary.

00:37:37.370 --> 00:37:39.420
Thank you. Now I can finish Goroku.

00:37:39.420 --> 00:37:41.780
T-That's impossible!

00:37:41.780 --> 00:37:43.990
There's still a spy among the police!

00:37:43.990 --> 00:37:48.750
I have the connections
so go escape overseas.

00:37:48.750 --> 00:37:50.340
Life's long, Natsumi-chan!

00:37:50.340 --> 00:37:52.740
Good things will still come your way!

00:37:52.740 --> 00:37:55.420
I see you still have a soft spot for Natsumi.

00:37:55.420 --> 00:37:58.840
That's because I refuse to be a cheater.

00:37:58.840 --> 00:38:00.770
Cheaters are real bastards.

00:38:00.770 --> 00:38:03.580
Nothing's worse than hurting your family.

00:38:03.580 --> 00:38:06.170
I don't lay a hand on married women.

00:38:06.170 --> 00:38:07.450
That's my motto.

00:38:07.450 --> 00:38:08.740
- Yes, Ma'am.
- What?

00:38:08.740 --> 00:38:11.910
Ignore me. I'm just humoring myself.

00:38:14.550 --> 00:38:16.380
I have a favor to ask of you, Kaieda-san.

00:38:16.380 --> 00:38:19.350
Another one?

00:38:20.110 --> 00:38:23.340
- Hello?
- I know the specifics of the deal.

00:38:23.340 --> 00:38:24.810
It's happening at 6PM tomorrow,

00:38:24.810 --> 00:38:29.430
at an office in Machida,
owned by Yaichi himself.

00:38:29.430 --> 00:38:30.700
Thank you.

00:38:30.700 --> 00:38:33.000
I'll get our investigation team moving.

00:38:33.000 --> 00:38:36.320
My husband has been kidnapped by Fuyuhashi.

00:38:37.960 --> 00:38:39.610
I know.

00:38:39.610 --> 00:38:42.660
I understand tomorrow's deal is your priority.

00:38:42.660 --> 00:38:46.740
Until then, you won't send out your forces.

00:38:48.300 --> 00:38:51.980
I will do whatever it takes
to keep my husband alive.

00:38:51.980 --> 00:38:56.950
So please, save him
once you've dealt with the deal.

00:38:57.690 --> 00:38:59.660
You have my word.

00:39:12.710 --> 00:39:15.580
My husband is still alive, right?

00:39:15.580 --> 00:39:17.480
He is, indeed.

00:39:17.480 --> 00:39:19.360
I still have a card up my sleeve.

00:39:19.360 --> 00:39:21.740
I'd like us to speak, in private.

00:39:23.520 --> 00:39:25.510
All right.

00:39:26.580 --> 00:39:31.680
I'll be waiting at our usual restaurant.

00:39:38.410 --> 00:39:40.350
Where is my husband?

00:39:47.440 --> 00:39:50.880
I was just about to speak to him.

00:40:04.270 --> 00:40:07.590
Hello? Can you hear us?

00:40:07.590 --> 00:40:11.010
"Desperate to escape the scene
after murdering his wife,"

00:40:11.010 --> 00:40:14.330
"Riku Hayase killed Inspector Gido
and took his place."

00:40:14.330 --> 00:40:18.500
"Yet unable to deal with the suspicions
from his fellow officers,"

00:40:18.500 --> 00:40:21.400
"he committed suicide
with an illegally procured gun."

00:40:21.400 --> 00:40:23.410
Wait, let me speak.

00:40:23.410 --> 00:40:25.060
Natsumi.

00:40:25.900 --> 00:40:27.640
Natsumi!

00:40:28.690 --> 00:40:30.540
Natsumi!

00:40:32.720 --> 00:40:34.300
[Mum, Takumi, I'm sorry]

00:40:34.300 --> 00:40:38.460
The police will realize
this whole scene was faked.

00:40:38.460 --> 00:40:40.120
Oh, they won't.

00:40:40.120 --> 00:40:43.940
I have a formidable ally within the force.

00:40:50.750 --> 00:40:52.010
What're you doing?

00:40:52.010 --> 00:40:53.950
Nothing important.

00:40:53.950 --> 00:40:56.580
I gotta give you credit, Adachi.

00:40:56.580 --> 00:40:58.940
Your hunch was on the mark.

00:40:58.940 --> 00:41:03.230
The fingerprints left on this photo
were of Riku Hayase.

00:41:03.230 --> 00:41:05.570
That man isn't Gido.

00:41:07.170 --> 00:41:09.340
He's Riku Hayase.

00:41:15.940 --> 00:41:19.120
And just when you two were reunited.

00:41:19.120 --> 00:41:21.930
Really, what a shame.

00:41:21.930 --> 00:41:27.410
You think everything will end tomorrow?

00:41:27.410 --> 00:41:32.560
I know the specifics of my deal
were leaked to the police.

00:41:34.010 --> 00:41:36.300
Please, come join us.

00:41:45.600 --> 00:41:47.810
Thank you for your patience, gentlemen.

00:41:52.380 --> 00:41:56.280
Excellent work, Natsumi-san.

00:41:56.280 --> 00:42:01.400
As you can see now, I was on this side.

00:42:02.220 --> 00:42:05.780
I'm glad I had you monitoring the police.

00:42:05.780 --> 00:42:08.640
Family truly is a reliable bond.

00:42:09.810 --> 00:42:15.230
You two never stood a chance.

00:42:18.010 --> 00:42:20.700
Please, save him.

00:42:20.700 --> 00:42:22.880
Please, I beg you.

00:42:22.880 --> 00:42:25.060
Please save my husband!

00:42:25.060 --> 00:42:26.790
I will die in his stead!

00:42:26.790 --> 00:42:28.540
Goroku-san, please.

00:42:28.540 --> 00:42:32.850
Can we do the rough handling elsewhere?

00:42:32.850 --> 00:42:35.230
We hear nothing.

00:42:35.230 --> 00:42:39.590
We've simply come to enjoy a meal.

00:42:39.590 --> 00:42:42.030
I am well aware.

00:42:42.030 --> 00:42:44.070
You're in the presence of important guests.

00:42:44.070 --> 00:42:46.350
Please, stay quiet.

00:42:47.350 --> 00:42:49.550
Fuyuhashi, I'm begging you.

00:42:50.310 --> 00:42:53.320
Say you killed me, and let me go.

00:42:53.320 --> 00:42:56.410
Then I'll get the jump on Goroku.

00:42:56.410 --> 00:42:58.070
Fuyuhashi!

00:42:59.540 --> 00:43:02.360
He's going to kill Natsumi.

00:43:03.860 --> 00:43:06.540
You don't want to be a killer, right?

00:43:06.540 --> 00:43:09.100
You want to save people.

00:43:15.130 --> 00:43:18.510
You think this will make Machi happy?

00:43:21.390 --> 00:43:23.540
I'm sorry.

00:43:24.340 --> 00:43:27.930
I couldn't make our dream come true.

00:43:37.820 --> 00:43:40.890
If I want to grant Machi's dream,

00:43:40.890 --> 00:43:43.790
I can't disobey Goroku-san's orders.

00:43:45.210 --> 00:43:47.990
You escaped on your own.

00:44:03.010 --> 00:44:04.660
Kiriya...

00:44:04.660 --> 00:44:07.570
Sorry, Goroku-san's orders.

00:44:07.570 --> 00:44:11.270
He told me to call Kikuchi-san,
just in case you betrayed him.

00:44:11.270 --> 00:44:17.420
Were you about to let him escape?

00:44:17.420 --> 00:44:20.250
Hey, wait...

00:44:20.250 --> 00:44:25.030
Goroku-san's orders are absolute.

00:44:32.570 --> 00:44:36.790
Save him, please! Please!

00:44:40.770 --> 00:44:42.630
Yaichi.

00:44:44.330 --> 00:44:49.720
You will roll back my demotion, yes?

00:44:52.080 --> 00:44:55.180
You'll lead the police.

00:44:55.180 --> 00:44:58.180
I'll lead the nation.

00:45:01.200 --> 00:45:03.300
To this country's bright future.

00:45:09.960 --> 00:45:19.940
Timing and subtitles by
"🍰 The Pastry Detectives 🔍" Team @Viki.com

00:45:19.940 --> 00:45:24.080
[Reboot, Last Day]

00:45:24.080 --> 00:45:29.290
[Reboot]

00:45:29.290 --> 00:45:32.740
Don't you want to see your Takumi-kun again?
[Next: the last chapter: Reboot]

00:45:32.740 --> 00:45:34.440
Of course I do.
[The last days of the couple that changed their faces for their family]

00:45:34.440 --> 00:45:36.090
I want to hold him close, and never let go.

00:45:36.090 --> 00:45:38.060
- You've become strong, kid.
- Dad?

00:45:38.060 --> 00:45:40.020
I'll have it ready by tomorrow.
[A turbulent fate. Is it a tearful ending that awaits them?]

00:45:40.020 --> 00:45:41.250
We must reboot this country.

00:45:41.250 --> 00:45:43.370
I was on this side.

00:45:43.370 --> 00:45:46.180
You'll regret making an enemy
of the Hayase's.

00:45:46.180 --> 00:45:47.360
Natsumi's not your enemy.

00:45:47.360 --> 00:45:50.210
- Natsumi!
- I will die in his stead!

00:45:50.210 --> 00:45:53.030
At least I got to see you.